  "content": "<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"__BG_COLOR__\",\"text\":\"__TEXT_COLOR__\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"40px\",\"right\":\"0px\",\"bottom\":\"40px\",\"left\":\"0px\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-text-color has-background\" style=\"background-color:__BG_COLOR__;color:__TEXT_COLOR__;padding-top:40px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:40px;padding-left:0px\">\n\n__LOGO_OR_SITENAME__\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"huge\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-huge-font-size\">Start your newsletter with an intro, sometimes known as a “topper”.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is where the lead writer or editor for the newsletter introduces the main storylines for the day.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"40px\",\"right\":\"0px\",\"bottom\":\"28px\",\"left\":\"0px\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull\" style=\"padding-top:40px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:28px;padding-left:0px\"><!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"15%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:15%\"><!-- wp:image {\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"is-style-rounded\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-style-rounded\"><img src=\"https://newspack.newspackstaging.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/pexels-dogukan-benli-1996760-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"width\":\"85%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"flex-basis:85%\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Robert Johnson</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Co-founder and Lead Columnist</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You might want to consider adding some bullet points to highlight the biggest stories of the day so that a reader can easily scan through this section. Those bullets could include:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Facts or figures about your community</li><li>Any notable news in your area — openings/closings of key businesses, for instance</li><li>And anything else you want to make sure readers definitely see</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"16px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:16px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:newspack-newsletters/posts-inserter {\"postsToShow\":4,\"innerBlocksToInsert\":[],\"featuredImageSize\":\"medium\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"newsletterVisibility\":\"email\",\"height\":\"16px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:16px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"newsletterVisibility\":\"email\",\"align\":\"full\",\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#fafafa\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"40px\",\"right\":\"0px\",\"bottom\":\"40px\",\"left\":\"0px\"}}}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-background\" style=\"padding-top:40px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:40px;padding-left:0px;background-color:#fafafa\">\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 id=\"support-our-newsroom\">Support our newsroom</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Make sure you have a call-to-action to support your work. This can be a few sentences like this, reminding readers of the value of your newsroom, or it can be an image. Either way, make sure you give a clear CTA and a unique link to track support back to this email.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button {\"className\":\"is-style-fill\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\">Support us</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->\n\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:group --><!-- wp:spacer {\"newsletterVisibility\":\"email\",\"height\":\"16px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:16px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:social-links {\"newsletterVisibility\":\"email\",\"align\":\"center\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\"}} -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-social-links aligncenter\"><!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"#\",\"service\":\"facebook\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"#\",\"service\":\"twitter\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"#\",\"service\":\"instagram\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:social-link {\"url\":\"#\",\"service\":\"youtube\"} /--></ul>\n<!-- /wp:social-links -->"
}
